{"word":"μάχαιρα","slug":"μάχαιρα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>μάχαιρα, ης, ἡ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μάχομαι\">μάχομαι</a></el>] ‘a relatively short weapon with a sharp blade’ (distinguished from the larger related weapon <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ῥομφαία\">ῥομφαία</a></el>), <b>sword, dagger <a href='B:470 26:47'>Mt 26:47</a>, <a href='B:470 26:52'>52</a>; <a href='B:490 21:24'>Lk 21:24</a>; <a href='B:490 22:38'>22:38</a>; <a href='B:500 18:10'>J 18:10f</a>; <a href='B:510 12:2'>Ac 12:2</a>; <a href='B:510 16:27'>16:27</a>; <a href='B:650 4:12'>Hb 4:12</a>; <a href='B:730 6:4'>Rv 6:4</a>.</b> In imagery <b><a href='B:470 10:34'>Mt 10:34</a>; <a href='B:520 8:35'>Ro 8:35</a></b> (of life-threatening experience); <b><a href='B:520 13:4'>13:4</a></b> (of judicial power); <b><a href='B:560 6:17'>Eph 6:17</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:Ματταθίας\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:μάχη\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}